<span id="freeTextContainer4729150006795088864">When I tell you this collection is so awesome it will make you think about how to still find truth within your personal journey toward King&apos;s vision of love. I have to tell you that I have been an adherent of King&apos;s teachings since I was first introduce to them in college. What King has shown me through the years is that no matter the steps we take to reconcile our past, we ultimately must continue the work of striving to reenvision our future. As he mentions in his conclusion: He had gotten sta</span>
  <span id="freeText4729150006795088864" style="display:none">When I tell you this collection is so awesome it will make you think about how to still find truth within your personal journey toward King's vision of love. I have to tell you that I have been an adherent of King's teachings since I was first introduce to them in college. What King has shown me through the years is that no matter the steps we take to reconcile our past, we ultimately must continue the work of striving to reenvision our future. As he mentions in his conclusion: He had gotten stabbed in Harlem during a book signing. And had he sneezed, he would have died. And if he had died then, would we have the future we have now? Will we have the knowledge we have now? These fundamental questions help to shape how I perceive the future, and what can be achieved in a New understanding of Self.</span>
